‚ú® NovelAI api python sdk with Pydantic.

The goal of this repository is to use Pydantic to build legitimate requests to access the NovelAI API service.

### Roadmap üöß

- [x] tool.random_prompt
- [x] tool.paint_mask
- [x] tool.image_metadata
- [x] /ai/generate-image
